SECTION 1. The following barrios are hereby created in the Municipality of Palapag, Province of Samar:

Barrio Campidico, consisting of the sitios of Tubay, Nasohong and Banica;

Barrio Magsaysay consisting of the sitios of Malihao, Napo and Cale;

Barrio Maragano, consisting of the sitios of Kalinawan, Canbisco, Mampogay, Cabotonan and Maitmait;

Barrio Nipa, consisting of the sitios of Doljogan, Libas, Cabarasan, Malobago, Dinodogho-an, Sumalidsid, Son-og and Panagdanan;

Barrio Bagacay, consisting of the sitios of Tubag, Pong-ol, Binatiklan, Manganino, Caghoguinog, Kanonghan, Paiigodtan, Cagomasam, Capdanogan, Guindago-an, Hiba-tuan, Can-irib and Borac;

Barrio Mabaras, consisting of the sitios of Camay-awan, Culipapa;

Barrio Binay, consisting of the sitios of Solangan, Lalangoyon, Doro-oñgan, Bungalon and Inom-enom;

Barrio Sumoroy, consisting of the sitios of Guin-parican, Tinampo, Guinpontingan, Cancalaton, Baho, Bo-lagsong and Salagan;

Barrio Sinalaran, consisting of the sitios of Labidao and Balud;

Barrio Paysud, consisting of the sitios of Cabonga-an, Danao, Nabatasan and Darag; and
